Hellplague:
 
Hellplague wanted to show the personal logs to Blacknightmare, it turned out to be Malice's ship, and the Malice in the logs was totally differant than the one they fought and later brainwashed.  He was so hateful, vulgar, almost evil.  It was easy to see he was a bounty hunter, and a good one, he had racked up easily over 986 bounties, adding up to who knew how much money in currency from across the galaxy.  Trully, they got him at a good time, when he was in a good mood.
 
"Amazing, Blacknightmare needs to this!"  
 
She closed the logs and went to go find her sister, and show her what she had seen.
